{"tid":1994960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：PK鄧下周赴立會「格鬥」 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-04-30T00:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T01:15:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b21f0a80bd8fd9096d656c9a4cebc941bb45171d","tid":1994960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200430/26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200430%2F26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=1753cad7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200430%2F26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM%2F&h=7e2d87dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200430/26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：PK鄧下周赴立會「格鬥」 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200430/large/1588179328_5b36.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200430%2Flarge%2F1588179328_5b36.gif&h=215b3b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇成龍戲學做警察嘅警務處處長鄧炳強，終於有機會喺立法會「獻技」。立法會保安事務委員會一早請咗PK鄧出席，交代2019年罪案情況，點知因為武漢肺炎爆發，會期一改再改，雖然PK鄧早前都出席過財委會特別委員會就警隊增開支解畫，但議員日始終唔夠時間針對警隊種種批評、尤其令人。。。。。要求PK鄧回應，下星期終於有機會嘞。<br />\n<br />\n勢與民主派擦出火花<br />\n<br />\n保安事務委員會5月5日、即係下周二開會，據聞PK鄧應承赴會。。。。由2點半開到5點。<br />\n<br />\n八方聽聞，自稱理直氣壯嘅PK鄧，等去立法會同議員「戰鬥」好耐，可能。。。。。會喺當日擦出火花。"},{"pid":"4f220930d5a0dcbf262e68137fc149bfcb21bf62","tid":1994960,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200430/26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200430%2F26UCTGQINWM64XS2F7JNGENVHM%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=1753c